These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, epic
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the owner of the cat##7
2. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
3. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | fantasy | martial-arts |
| Pet           | cat  | rabbit     | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, trance, hip-hop
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, motorbike
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the person driving the boat##7
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | d&b | hip-hop |
| Transport     | boat       | motorbike     | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, iced-tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, ship, scooter
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person driving the jet-ski##7
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | cola | lemonade | iced-tea  |
| Transport   | scooter  | ship  | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, videographer, musician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, drama, crime
1. the fisherman is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the videographer##7
2. the person watching drama movies is not the fisherman##6
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | videographer | fisherman | musician     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama    | western          | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, classical
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway
1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the fan of dubstep##7
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | classical     | dubstep   |
| Transport     | subway | scooter | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, indie, house
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, british, polish
1. the italian is on the left or right of the british##3
2. the british is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
3. the fan of indie is on the right of the polish##1
4. the fan of indie is somewhere between the polish and the fan of salsa##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | house    | indie     | salsa     |
| Nationality   | polish | british | italian |

