.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, horse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, rugby, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | horse       | turtle      | fish       |
| Sport   | snowboarding | soccer | rugby |

