The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, crime, animation
1. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the lawyer##7
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | engineer | dancer  | lawyer |
| Movie-Genre   | animation      | horror | crime      |

