.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, singing, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, security-guard, freelancer
1. the freelancer is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
2. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the electrician is somewhere between the security-guard and the person who's hobby is singing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | singing | video-games | photography   |
| Job     | freelancer    | electrician  | security-guard |

