.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, snowboarding
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's sport is volleyball##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | tea    | cola |
| Sport      | snowboarding | swimming | volleyball |

