.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, spinach, corn
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, family
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person eating cranberry##7
3. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | cranberry  | corn       | spinach     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | satire | adventure |

