.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, 7up
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, journalist, chef
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person drinking water and the journalist##7
3. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | water      | 7up     | hot-chocolate |
| Job        | chef | paramedic | journalist    |

 